import React, { useContext } from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

import { UrlsContext } from '../contexts/UrlsContext'

import Layout from '../components/Layout/index'

import Header from '../components/Index Page/Header/index'
import CardList from '../components/Index Page/CardSection/index'
import AboutSection from '../components/Index Page/AboutSection'
import ApiSection from '../components/Index Page/ApiSection'

const Wrapper = styled.div`
  display: grid;
`

const IndexPage = () => {
  return (
    <Layout>
      <Wrapper>
        <Header />
        <CardList />
        <AboutSection />
        <ApiSection />
      </Wrapper>
    </Layout>
  )
}

export default IndexPage
